name: Pirotess (Record of Lodoss War) NSFW / SFW
description:
Hello my elven enjoyers!

Today we have another Dark elf and this is Pirotess from retro epic anime Record of Lodoss War.

She is also seductive dark elf, I suppose you like her :3

NSFW / SFW Model

LoRA was trained on Animefull-pruned.cpkt due to best compitability with all anime checkpoint models.

0.8 - 1 strength of Lora is the best radius. I prefer 0.9 and 0.8 for NSFW poses with other LoRAs.

Some necessary tokens for better experience:

Pirotess, dark skinned female, dark skin, pointy ears, white hair, long hair, circlet, lipstick, makeup, black eyeshadow, jewelry, bracelet, yellow eyes,
huge breasts, cleavage

Recommended:

Ultra detail hair, ultra detail face, blue eyes, perfect eyes, perfect face,

Optional:

holding weapon, holding sword

Clothes:
white short dress, white gloves, thigh boots,

Also LoRA trained with some NSFW poses. So you can try it with LoRAs or without it.

Advices for better experience:

·         use highres.fix (If you are sure that your prompt is easy for SD); I prefer x4_Fatal_anime_500000_G, lollypop and animesharp.

use extention "dddetailer" (very useful extension for faces. You forget about face inpainting with it).

·         use SD Upscale script in img2img (For me 1.25-1.5x with AnimeSharp, UltraSharp or fatal anime is good on 0.2-0.3 denoising strengh);

·         use Ultimate SD Upscale script in img2img with controlnet (tile) for more details if you upscale to 4K or more.

·         Use inpaint and sketch (or Photopea) for other details;

·         Use Photoshop / Photopea extension.

I will be glad to receive feedback from you and a demonstration of your art with my LoRA!
